        <mxCell id="tnEm9dg9qmmmI9w5VtZP-5" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="1.User should be able to login.&lt;div&gt;2.User should be able to search the product of will.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3.User shoul have a cart service where he/she can add product of will.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4.User should be able to check order status.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5.User should be able to place order and check out(payment).&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="110" width="390" x="80" y="140" as="geometry" />
